}
```

Here, instead of creating a regular expression with the letter to be replaced, the code uses the `indexOf()` method to find the position of the first occurrence of the letter in the sentence. If the letter is found, it is replaced with an underscore character using the `replace()` method. This continues until all occurrences of the letter have been replaced. Finally, the total count of replaced letters is calculated by counting the number of successful replacements.

